# EconVista Pro â€“ Economic Intelligence Platform

EconVista Pro is an economic data visualization project that presents key macroeconomic indicators through an interactive web dashboard. The project combines data analysis and frontend visualization to transform raw economic data into clear, readable insights.

## Overview
The project focuses on analyzing and visualizing economic indicators such as GDP growth, inflation rates, employment levels, trade balance, and development metrics. Data is processed and prepared using Python, then displayed through a static frontend dashboard built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features
- Interactive economic dashboard
- Summary metric cards showing latest values and trends
- Line charts for time-series analysis
- Tabular view of the complete dataset
- Light and dark mode support
- Responsive layout for different screen sizes

